your next app. I want to come back to one important aspect of QueryChat, though, which is

00:13:41.840 --> 00:13:49.440
safety. Because is this safe? And yeah, it's a fair question. But luckily, QueryChat is designed

00:13:49.440 --> 00:13:56.880
entirely around control. The LLM never executes anything itself. It never touches your database

00:13:56.880 --> 00:14:04.479
or data, and it never sees the raw data. Its only job is to propose read-only SQL. If you ask to

00:14:04.479 --> 00:14:11.039
