00:14:17.919 --> 00:14:24.000
database, DuckDB or your own, that only provides read-only access, and your data will be left

00:14:24.000 --> 00:14:30.479
untouched. So, no destructive actions on your production database when you set QueryChat's

00:14:30.479 --> 00:14:38.239
